  Single source of truth for the user-facing app label. Reference from
  AndroidManifest.xml as `@string/app_name`. Add locale-specific
  values/values-<lang>/strings.xml when we localize the app label.

  The `applicationId` (final: club.prism.mobile) lives in
  android/app/build.gradle.kts and is separate from this label.
-->
